g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22aec815566ff7ac642e8a60181fa76399106d18","tid":944131,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T06:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c566c0c49180897b091ea91435ecbdef298ccc","tid":944131,"uid":73112,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T06:16:47.000Z","msg":"呢啲成日誘惑人既大奶賤女人一定要好好教訓下<br />\n起勢咁聞佢對大肉腳啲香味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再含佢腳趾舔佢腳板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好就一一邊踩住我臉一邊囂張咁屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用碌鳩頂佢腳板底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個大屁股又大又白 格肋底又滑又香 仲有對賤腳 質個頭入去索 舔到佢啲淫肉全部都係口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用佢對淫賤大奶同大臀肉打我臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用碌鳩打磨拍佢塊淫臉+奶 令佢成身都充滿住碌鳩嘅雄性味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用兩塊大臀肉同大波波玩臀交奶交同腋交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗仔式打屁股一邊打一邊問喺咪淫婦喺咪成日故意露奶誘惑人屌佢 再屌到佢叫老公 邊問邊大大力打佢個大屁股 再屌到佢個大屁股搖黎搖去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女下男上張腿當打椿機咁屌 最好屌一下啲淫水擠一大堆出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從佢背後用手托開對淫腳令佢正面咁屌 等佢自己睇睇下啲淫水幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中出之餘一定要射到佢成身都係精 再用有殘餘精液嘅大龜頭拍佢臉+磨嘴唇<br />\n最後塞入口等佢舔乾淨 令佢變成性奴液便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2<br />\n2"},{"pid":"8c64375ac292a09e548f158dccc7e5bc26a690ad","tid":944131,"uid":10890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6cf7a464a7512e7949711e926888f0c958eede09","tid":944131,"uid":114110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T05:37:59.000Z","msg":"你地見大波先攬姐，catgirl就由佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T06:26:33.000Z","msg":"Catgirl嘅話我一腳伸佢落去就差唔多"},{"pid":"b780a0c3c12ba91353f480e4d8cd2af825861f3e","tid":944131,"uid":30186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T06:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c8020c9f6c3a49898986e424bbc985b54c13c3","tid":944131,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T07:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0531f26c105c25d777aa21617ed4c4a0c66515c2","tid":944131,"uid":57170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T07:26:35.000Z","msg":"地方媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16dfc60f6392db1c5dc49e1fe3ed4a3bf715be78","tid":944131,"uid":222807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T07:32:09.000Z","msg":"咁撚正都要跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40dd1ba8c0644eefd4bfeeb66ed4cc912deed345","tid":944131,"uid":1248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"香港唔係冇救人<br />\n反而係將救人講成阻人自殺正仆街"},{"pid":"d9a1193a1337f72f3ab4b1e882eaf8f3cf0ca4c4","tid":944131,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:06:39.000Z","msg":"同我扑野唔好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da92c1e200b7b0498523d084caf7181b68d7af07","tid":944131